re. You will be behind Chainlink's public brand and work directly with our CMO and executive team to strategize, design, and execute the communications strategy for our product globally. Responsibilities Create a compelling brand message and thought leadership point of view; shape the global narrative around smart contracts and Chainlink's role within it Develop and execute a world-class media strategy that shares the Chainlink story across the international business, trade (blockchain / tech) and mainstream press Oversee all external communications including Chainlink product launches and third party ecosystem announcements with partners, projects, node operators, integrators, users, etc. Oversee creation of a large range of content including press releases, media pitches, and all other materials required to support communications, public relations, and analyst relations strategies Partner with our PR agency to drive meaningful coverage across press, podcast, video and other media Strengthen the relationships with top research analysts through one-on-one engagements, briefings, and proactive outreaches Create and execute a comprehensive global content strategy; work with country managers to localize content across various geographies Oversee social media strategy (Twitter, etc.) Manage speaking opportunities at conferences and other in-person events Oversee the execution of the Smart Contract Summit developer and community conference Collaborate with the executive team to develop their point of view and provide media training/coaching as needed to help establish them as experts in the field Develop a crisis communications practice and playbook Build and lead a team of exceptional communications professionals; manage a team of writers, videographers, press agencies, social media managers, event organizers and content producers Bachelor\u2019s degree or above 7+ years of experience in communications, marketing or related fields Exceptional written, oral, interpersonal, and storytelling skills to express messages concisely and compellingly A demonstrated ability to understand a complex technical subject matter and to simplify and explain it to a broader audience Demonstrate grace under fire and ability to work in a fast-paced working environment, ability to deliver a quality product under time-bound and stressful circumstances A proven track record of building long-term, beneficial relationships with media and analysts Experience successfully managing agencies, clients and/or direct reports Experience working with global companies with and audience bases in multiple languages Experience working on developer tools, technical products, and open-source a plus Ability to keep up to date with the latest news and discoveries in the blockchain and technology space Passion for the blockchain space and its power to change the world for the better This role is location agnostic anywhere in the world. Though we ask that you overlap some working hours with Eastern Standard Time (EST). Chainlink is an Equal Opportunity Employer.* Show full job description Quick Apply Stay Connected Contact Us SimplyHired Blog Facebook Twitter LinkedIn YouTube Job Tools Local Jobs Salary Estimator Post Jobs Free Resume Builder Browse All Jobs All Salaries All Cities All Companies Guides Resumes Cover Letters Interviews Careers Take your job search wherever you go. United States United StatesCanada ArgentinaAustraliaBelgiÃ«BrasilDeutschlandEspaÃ±aFranceIndiaIrelandItaliaMÃ©xicoNederlandÃsterreichPortugalSchweizSouth AfricaSverigeUnited KingdomÐ Ð¾ÑÑÐ¸Ñíêµ­ä¸­å½æ¥æ¬ Â© 2020 SH Inc. | Privacy | TermsÂ |Â Privacy Center |Â Do Not Sell My Personal Information"
